<h4 id="youtube">YouTube</h4>

<p>


<a href="http://localhost:4000/images/other/switch/youtube.jpg" target="_blank">
<img src="http://localhost:4000/images/other/switch/youtube.jpg" alt="YouTube" title="YouTube" />
</a>



</p>

<p><a href="https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/youtube-switch/">YouTube</a> is not a game. But I run it really frequently. Switch is very silent, always connected to the TV/monitor, always booted into the operating system. So it‚Äôs no need to wait while PC boots for a dinner - just run YouTube on your Switch.</p>

<h2 id="conclusion">Conclusion</h2>

<p>Nintendo Switch games are usually not about high-end AAA graphics. There are not many fighting games. But you could find a lot of good kind games focused on the gameplay.</p>
